config DRM_VENUE8_DISPLAY
	tristate "Dell Venue 8 3840 Tangier MIPI DSI display"
	depends on DRM && PCI && X86
	select DRM_KMS_HELPER
	select DRM_GEM_SHMEM_HELPER
	help
	  DRM driver for the Dell Venue 8 3840's MIPI DSI display panel
	  (1200x1920 AUO/Innolux). The display controller is part of the
	  Merrifield (Tangier) SoC's PowerVR G6400 GPU PCI device.

	  This driver provides a simple framebuffer console via
	  drm_simple_display_pipe. It does not provide GPU acceleration.

	  If unsure, say N.
